							<ownedComment xmi:type='uml:Comment' xmi:id='Activities-CompleteStructuredActivities-LoopNode-bodyOutput-_ownedComment.0' body='A list of output pins within the body fragment the values of which are moved to the loop variable pins after completion of execution of the body, before the next iteration of the loop begins or before the loop exits.'>
