						<ownedComment xmi:type='uml:Comment' xmi:id='Deployments-Artifacts-Artifact-_ownedComment.0' body='An artifact is the specification of a physical piece of information that is used or produced by a software development process, or by deployment and operation of a system. Examples of artifacts include model files, source files, scripts, and binary executable files, a table in a database system, a development deliverable, or a word-processing document, a mail message.'>
							<annotatedElement xmi:idref='Deployments-Artifacts-Artifact'/>
