							<ownedComment xmi:type='uml:Comment' xmi:id='Deployments-Artifacts-Artifact-manifestation-_ownedComment.0' body='The set of model elements that are manifested in the Artifact. That is, these model elements are utilized in the construction (or generation) of the artifact.'>
